item.title: CVE-2021-3555|2024-09-17T03:08:09.236Z -- eufy -- indoor%202k%20indoor%20camera
item.description: A Buffer Overflow vulnerability in the RSTP server component of Eufy Indoor 2K Indoor Camera allows a local attacker to achieve remote code execution. This issue affects: Eufy Indoor 2K Indoor Camera 2.0.9.3 version and prior versions.
